'''艾伦望远镜阵'''（{{lang-en|'''Allen Telescope Array'''}}，缩写为{{lang|en|'''ATA'''}}）先前以'''公顷望远镜'''（{{lang-en|'''One Hectare Telescope'''}}，缩写为{{lang|en|'''1hT'''}}）而闻名，是由[[SETI协会|SETI协会]]及[[射电天文学实验室|射电天文学实验室]]在[[加州大学伯克利分校|加州大学伯克利分校]]合力建造的[[射电干涉仪|射电干涉仪]]，致力于进行天文观测和[[搜寻地外文明计划|搜寻外星文明]]。<ref>{{cite news | author=[[Daniel_Terdiman|Daniel Terdiman]] | url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-13772_3-10121889-52.html | title=SETI's large-scale telescope scans the skies | date=12 December 2008 | work=CNET News | accessdate=2008-12-12 | archive-date=2014-02-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201143419/http://news.cnet.com/8301-13772_3-10121889-52.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author=John Johnson, Jr. | url=http://www.latimes.com/news/printedition/front/la-sci-seti1-2008jun01,0,1621324.story | title=Aliens get a new switchboard: a SETI radio telescope in Northern California | date=1 June 2008 | work=The Los Angeles Times | accessdate=2008-09-29 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081004224517/http://www.latimes.com/news/printedition/front/la-sci-seti1-2008jun01,0,1621324.story | archivedate=2008年10月4日 | deadurl=no }}</ref>加州大学伯克利分校自2012年4月脱离该项目<ref>{{cite web | author=Robert Sanders | title=UC Berkeley passes management of Allen Telescope Array to SRI | url=http://newscenter.berkeley.edu/2012/04/13/uc-berkeley-passes-management-of-allen-telescope-array-to-sri/ | publisher=UC Berkeley  NewsCenter | date=April 13, 2012 | accessdate=29 December 2012 | archive-date=2013-10-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023061917/http://newscenter.berkeley.edu/2012/04/13/uc-berkeley-passes-management-of-allen-telescope-array-to-sri/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，设备当前由独立、非营利性的研究机构[[SRI国际|SRI国际]]进行管理。

艾伦望远镜阵正在由[[哈特克里射电天文台|哈特克里射电天文台]]负责建造中，距离加利福尼亚[[圣弗朗西斯科|圣弗朗西斯科]]东北部{{convert|290|mi}}。建成之后，该阵列预计由350架天线组成。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://archive.seti.org/pdfs/Shostak-spring2009-EnS.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-02-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415115307/http://archive.seti.org/pdfs/Shostak-spring2009-EnS.pdf |archivedate=2015-04-15 }}</ref>第一阶段42架天线（ATA-42）在2007年11月11日建造完成并开始运作。<ref name="NYT10-07">{{cite news | author=Dennis Overbye | title=Stretching the Search for Signs of Life | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/11/science/11seti.html | work=The New York Times | date=11 October 2007 | accessdate=2009-04-14 | archive-date=2021-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417181357/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/11/science/11seti.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author=Staff writers | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/7041183.stm | title=Skies to be swept for alien life | date=12 October 2007 | work=BBC News | accessdate=2007-10-12 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012223754/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/7041183.stm | archivedate=2007年10月12日 | deadurl=no }}</ref> 然而到2011年4月，由于资金短缺而被暂时搁置。<ref>{{cite web |last=Hardy |first=Michael |url=http://fcw.com/articles/2011/04/29/seti-shuts-down-telescopes-due-to-funding-cuts.aspx?s=fcwdaily_020511 |title=Federal Computer Week |publisher=Fcw.com |date=2011-04-29 |accessdate=2011-09-19 |archive-date=2018-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127130432/https://fcw.com/articles/2011/04/29/seti-shuts-down-telescopes-due-to-funding-cuts.aspx?s=fcwdaily_020511 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SETI">{{cite web |url=http://archive.seti.org/pdfs/ATA-hibernation.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-04-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303185340/http://archive.seti.org/pdfs/ATA-hibernation.pdf |archivedate=2016-03-03 }}</ref>直到2011年8月获得短期资金支持后<ref>{{cite web | author=John Cook | title=Search for ET continues as Paul Allen-backed telescope hits short-term funding goal | url=http://www.geekwire.com/2011/search-continues-paul-allenbacked-telescope-array-hits-shortterm-funding-goal | publisher= | date=August 7, 2011 | accessdate=29 December 2012 | archive-date=2018-11-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127125018/https://www.geekwire.com/2011/search-continues-paul-allenbacked-telescope-array-hits-shortterm-funding-goal/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，艾伦望远镜阵才于2011年12月5日重新恢复运作。<ref name=seti905>{{cite press release | title=SETI Search Resumes at Allen Telescope Array, Targeting New Planets | url=http://www.seti.org/node/905 | publisher=SETI Institute | date=December 5, 2011 | accessdate=29 December 2012 | archive-date=2011-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111208040312/http://www.seti.org/node/905 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

